https://w3id.org/babelon/comment.value: label of HP:0009736 (Tibial pseudoarthrosis)  ; abnormality of limbs ; abnormality of the skeletal system

value.value: "Pseudoartróza, nebo ""pakloub"" tibie je výsledkem vývojové vady tibie, která vede k spontánní fraktuře s neschopností vytvoření normálního kostního callusu (svalku). Kostní úlomky se nespojí, jsou spojené vazivovou tkání. Fraktura je zřídka přítomná při porodu, obvykle se projevý během prvních 18 měsících života."

https://w3id.org/babelon/source_value.value: "Pseudarthrosis, or ""false joint"" of the tibia is the result of a developmental failure in the tibia progressing to spontaneous fracture and subsequent fibrous nonunion. The fracture is rarely present at birth but commonly develops during the first 18 months of life."

https://w3id.org/babelon/comment.value: label of HP:0009775 (Amniotic constriction ring)  ; abnormality of prenatal development or birth

value.value: Annular constrictions around the digits, limbs, or trunk, occurring congenitally (sometimes causing intrauterine autoamputation) and also associated with a wide variety of disorders. Constrictive amniotic bands are the result of primary amniotic rupture, which can lead to entanglement of fetal tissue (especially limbs) in fibrous amniotic strands.

Doğuştan oluşan (bazen intrauterin otomatik amputasyona neden olan) ve aynı zamanda çok çeşitli bozukluklarla ilişkili olan parmakların, ekstremitelerin veya gövdelerin çevresinde halka şeklinde daralması. Konstriktif amniotik bantlar, fetal dokunun (özellikle ekstremitelerin) lifli amniyotik ipliklerde dolaşmasına neden olabilen primer amniyotik rüptürün sonucudur

https://w3id.org/babelon/source_value.value: Annular constrictions around the digits, limbs, or trunk, occurring congenitally (sometimes causing intrauterine autoamputation) and also associated with a wide variety of disorders. Constrictive amniotic bands are the result of primary amniotic rupture, which can lead to entanglement of fetal tissue (especially limbs) in fibrous amniotic strands.

value.value: Prstencovitá konstrikce kolem prstů, končetin, nebo trupu, vyskytující se kongenitálně (někdy způsobuje intrauterinní autoamputaci) a také asociovaná s širokou škálou nemocí. Konstriktivní amniotické pásy jsou výsledkem primárního natržení amnia, které může vést k uvíznutí fetální tkáně (zejména končetin) mezi fibrózní pruhy amnia

https://w3id.org/babelon/comment.value: label of HP:0009780 (Iliac horns)  ; abnormality of the skeletal system

value.value: Horn-like malformations of the iliac crests with symmetrical bilateral central posterior iliac processes. A characteristic finding in the Nail-Patella syndrome. Iliac horns are visible on X-ray and may be palpable, but are asymptomatic.

Simüküler iki taraflı merkezde olan kıça yakın kalça kemiğine ait işlemler ile kalça kemiği sorguçlarının boynuz gibi bozuklukları. Nail-Patella sendromunda karakteristik bir bulgu. Kalça kemiği boynuzları röntgen filminde görülebilir ve elle tutulabilir, ancak asemptomatiktir

https://w3id.org/babelon/source_value.value: Horn-like malformations of the iliac crests with symmetrical bilateral central posterior iliac processes. A characteristic finding in the Nail-Patella syndrome. Iliac horns are visible on X-ray and may be palpable, but are asymptomatic.

value.value: Výrůstky ve tvaru rohů na hranách ilické kostí, které jsou symetrické, bilaterální a na posteriorní části kosti. Jsou typických nálezem o Nail-Patella syndromu. Ilické rohy jsou patrné a rentgenovém snímku a mohou být i hmatné, nicméně jedná se o benigní nález.

https://w3id.org/babelon/source_value.value: Horn-like malformations of the iliac crests with symmetrical bilateral central posterior iliac processes. A characteristic finding in the Nail-Patella syndrome. Iliac horns are visible on X-ray and may be palpable, but are asymptomatic.
